    "body": "I have noticed that it would be better to have such a simple tool as decorator in code base to terminate port running by app.\n\nA simple example:\n\n```\nfrom flask import Flask\n\napp = Flask(__name__)\n\n@app.reboot()\n@app.route(\"/\")\ndef hello():\n    return \"Hello world\"\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    app.run()\n```\n",
